Third-party notice

This project currently depends on `animal-island-ui`
(https://github.com/guokaigdg/animal-island-ui), which is licensed under
Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International (CC BY-NC 4.0).

That component library does not permit commercial use under its license.
Using callai for personal / non-commercial purposes is fine with the current
UI dependency. Commercial redistribution of a build that still bundles
`animal-island-ui` requires either:

1. replacing that UI dependency with a differently licensed stack, or
2. obtaining a separate commercial license / permission from the library author.

Bundled brand art under `assets/brand/`, `src/assets/elements/`, and
`src-tauri/icons/` is original project artwork for callai unless noted
otherwise in those directories.
